author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Deus Ex is a game that is near and dear to my heart and it's getting remastered. This remaster however is surprisingly so low effort that when it was showed on State of Play I had to double check if this was actually real, sadly it is and you can pre-order this right now. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Worst Video Game Remaster Just Dropped...
